FBIS3-55708 "drsov007_r_94008" FBIS-SOV-94-007 Document Type:Daily Report 11 Jan 1994 Azerbaijan TV Carries Iranian-Produced Azeri Program NC0701154394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran in Turkish 1630 GMT 6 Jan 94 NC0701154394 Tehran Voice of the Islamic Republic of Iran Language: Turkish Article Type:BFN [Text] Azerbaijan's television network has begun to telecast a program by the Iranian television network in the Azeri language. The telecasting of the program began on Tuesday [4 January]. The 60-minute program will be telecast daily, from 1330 to 1430 Baku time -- that is, from 1300 to 1400 Tehran time. It includes Koranic recitations and political, social, and cultural news.
